{"content": "I need to multiply 322 \u00d7 352 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 322\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 243 + 18 + 2 = 263\u2081\u2080\n- 352\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 243 + 45 + 2 = 290\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 263 \u00d7 290 = 76,270\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 76270 \u00f7 9 = 8474 r 4\n- 8474 \u00f7 9 = 941 r 5\n- 941 \u00f7 9 = 104 r 5\n- 104 \u00f7 9 = 11 r 5\n- 11 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 2\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **125554\u2089**\n\n125554", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 342}